<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>5824</hymn_number>
<author>ạ̉myr smyr, kyrls ạlfy̱</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr - (yạ mṭmn qlby yạ yswʿ bạlḍyq wạlạ̹kẖtbạr
 myn gẖyrk byṭmn qlby lmạ ạ̉kwn mḥtạr)2
 1- (lmạ bkwn fy wsṭ ạlḍyq mạ bsẖwfsẖ zyk yạ yswʿ
 fy ạlṭryq ạ̉ʿz ṣdyq tryḥ ạlqlb ạlmwjwʿ)2
 2- (lmạ ʿynyạ tlmḥ ṣwrtk bḥs brạḥh jwạyạ
 wbḥs ạ̹ny tḥt rʿạytk wạ̹nk mạsẖy mʿạyạ)2
 3- (lmạ ạ̉ḥtạjk blqạk jnby tyjy tṭmn rwḥy byk
 lmạ bsẖwfk yrtạḥ qlby ʿlsẖạn bsẖky hmwmy lyk)2</lyrics>
<title>mṭmn qlby̱</title>
</song>